travelAgencyModel

Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • travelAgencyModel.Customer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Customer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Customer class containing basic information about a customer such as name and phone number. The Customer class implements PassengerList to keep track of any Passengers that this Customer might have paid for. Implements Serializable.
    Author:
    DVN
    See Also:
